    About

    YehChe

    A Taiwanese artist who uses video as his creative medium.

    Che has a wide range of works that include video art, films, music videos and theatre.His works draw inspiration from personal experiences and emotion which are all based on production point of view of images. Che uses different types of media to create his works. In doing so, he seeks to express the collective consciousness of human beings through art.

    ​

    葉澈

    影像藝術家，創作領域包括電影、錄像、MV、劇場、攝影、音像表演。多從影像的產製方式著手，以不同的媒材本質，尋找個人情感或者人類共同經驗，創作出企及集體意識的作品。目前專注於使用影像進入空間敘事的不同可能。

    1991  Born in Taipei, Taiwan
